    <div class="mainInfoPage">
        <dl>
            <dt>Customers</dt>
            <dd>The Customers page shows a table of the existing customers and can be used to add a new customer and
                update or delete an existing customer.</dd>
            <dt>Sneakers</dt>
            <dd>The Sneakers page shows a table of the sneaker inventory. Add a new sneaker and update or delete an
                existing sneaker.</dd>
            <dt>Orders</dt>
            <dd>The Orders page displays the order history table. Add order entries and update or delete existing
                orders.</dd>
            <dt>Raffles</dt>
            <dd>The Raffles page contains information about each raffle. Add a new raffle entry and update or delete an
                existing raffle.</dd>
            <dt>Drawings</dt>
            <dd>The Drawings page shows the date and day of each raffle. Add a new drawing entry and update or delete
                existing drawings.</dd>
            <dt>Sneaker Orders</dt>
            <dd>The Sneaker Orders page shows a table of the orders, which sneakers were purchased, and the quantity
                sold. Add a new transaction, and update or delete existing sneaker orders.</dd>
            <dt>Raffle Orders</dt>
            <dd>The Raffle Orders page shows a table of the orders and the raffle entries that were sold during the
                order. Add a new transaction, and update or delete existing raffle orders.</dd>
            <dt>Customer Raffles</dt>
            <dd>The Customer Raffles page contains information about each raffle, the customers who bought an entry, and
                each winner. Add a new customer raffle entry, and update or delete existing customer raffle entries.
            </dd>
        </dl>
